# FluxLoop CLI

Command-line interface for running agent simulations and managing FluxLoop workflows.

## Installation

```bash
pip install fluxloop-cli
```

## Quick Start

```bash
# Initialize a new FluxLoop project
fluxloop init

# Run agent simulations
fluxloop run

# Generate test inputs
fluxloop generate

# Check status
fluxloop status
```

